      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good high-level overview, but I'm looking for more specifics. Could you detail some of the actual studies or specific researchers who have argued for the genetic/biological side of the argument? I want to understand the specific data points or methodologies they use to support the idea of inherent differences.",
